<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Site Clarity</title>
  <meta name="description" content="Clear, accessible websites for small businesses.">
  <style>
    * {
      box-sizing: border-box;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
    }

    body {
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      line-height: 1.6;
      color: #1f1f1f;
      background: #f7f7f7;
    }

    .wrapper {
      width: 100%;
      max-width: 1100px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 0 20px;
    }

    header {
      background: #ffffff;
      border-bottom: 1px solid #e5e5e5;
      position: sticky;
      top: 0;
      z-index: 100;
    }

    .nav {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: center;
      padding: 18px 0;
      gap: 16px;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
    }

    .logo {
      font-size: 1.4rem;
      font-weight: bold;
      color: #111111;
      text-decoration: none;
    }

    .nav-links {
      display: flex;
      gap: 18px;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
    }

    .nav-links a {
      text-decoration: none;
      color: #333333;
      font-size: 0.95rem;
    }

    .hero {
      padding: 64px 0 48px;
      background: #ffffff;
    }

    .hero-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1.2fr 1fr;
      gap: 32px;
      align-items: center;
    }

    .hero h1 {
      font-size: 3rem;
      line-height: 1.1;
      margin-bottom: 16px;
      color: #111111;
    }

    .hero p {
      font-size: 1.1rem;
      margin-bottom: 24px;
      color: #444444;
      max-width: 650px;
    }

    .buttons {
      display: flex;
      gap: 14px;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
    }

    .btn {
      display: inline-block;
      text-decoration: none;
      padding: 14px 20px;
      border-radius: 8px;
      font-weight: bold;
      text-align: center;
    }

    .btn-primary {
      background: #111111;
      color: #ffffff;
    }

    .btn-secondary {
      background: #f1f1f1;
      color: #111111;
      border: 1px solid #d8d8d8;
    }

    .hero-card {
      background: #f4f4f4;
      border: 1px solid #e3e3e3;
      border-radius: 14px;
      padding: 24px;
    }

    .hero-card h2 {
      font-size: 1.2rem;
      margin-bottom: 14px;
    }

    .hero-card ul {
      padding-left: 20px;
    }

    .hero-card li {
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }

    section {
      padding: 56px 0;
    }

    .section-title {
      font-size: 2rem;
      margin-bottom: 14px;
      color: #111111;
    }

    .section-intro {
      max-width: 750px;
      margin-bottom: 28px;
      color: #555555;
    }

    .cards {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
      gap: 20px;
    }

    .card {
      background: #ffffff;
      border: 1px solid #e5e5e5;
      border-radius: 14px;
      padding: 24px;
    }

    .card h3 {
      font-size: 1.2rem;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }

    .card p {
      color: #555555;
    }

    .about {
      background: #ffffff;
    }

    .contact {
      background: #111111;
      color: #ffffff;
    }

    .contact p {
      max-width: 700px;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
      color: #e7e7e7;
    }

    .contact a {
      color: #ffffff;
    }

    footer {
      background: #0d0d0d;
      color: #cccccc;
      padding: 24px 0;
      font-size: 0.95rem;
    }

    @media (max-width: 900px) {
      .hero-grid {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      }

      .cards {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
      }

      .hero h1 {
        font-size: 2.4rem;
      }
    }

    @media (max-width: 600px) {
      .nav {
        align-items: flex-start;
      }

      .nav-links {
        width: 100%;
      }

      .hero {
        padding: 40px 0 32px;
      }

      .hero h1 {
        font-size: 2rem;
      }

      .hero p {
        font-size: 1rem;
      }

      .cards {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      }

      .section-title {
        font-size: 1.6rem;
      }

      .btn {
        width: 100%;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

  <header>
    <div class="wrapper nav">
      <a href="#" class="logo">Site Clarity</a>
      <nav class="nav-links">
        <a href="#services">Services</a>
        <a href="#about">About</a>
        <a href="#contact">Contact</a>
      </nav>
    </div>
  </header>

  <main>
    <section class="hero">
      <div class="wrapper hero-grid">
        <div>
          <h1>Clear websites for real people</h1>
          <p>
            Site Clarity helps small businesses make websites easier to understand, easier to use and more likely to turn visitors into enquiries.
          </p>
          <div class="buttons">
            <a href="#contact" class="btn btn-primary">Get in touch</a>
            <a href="#services" class="btn btn-secondary">See services</a>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="hero-card">
          <h2>What this means in practice</h2>
          <ul>
            <li>Clearer wording</li>
            <li>Better page structure</li>
            <li>Simple mobile friendly layouts</li>
            <li>Accessibility focused improvements</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section id="services">
      <div class="wrapper">
        <h2 class="section-title">Services</h2>
        <p class="section-intro">
          Support for businesses that need a website to explain what they do clearly and give customers confidence to get in touch.
        </p>

        <div class="cards">
          <div class="card">
            <h3>Website review</h3>
            <p>
              A clear review of what is confusing, what is working and what should change first.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="card">
            <h3>Content clarity</h3>
            <p>
              Rewriting web copy into plain English so visitors quickly understand your service.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="card">
            <h3>Page structure</h3>
            <p>
              Organising sections, headings and calls to action so the site feels simple and logical.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section id="about" class="about">
      <div class="wrapper">
        <h2 class="section-title">About Site Clarity</h2>
        <p class="section-intro">
          Good websites are not just about visuals. They need to make sense quickly. Site Clarity focuses on the gap between what a business wants to say and what users actually need to read.
        </p>
        <p>
          The aim is simple. Clearer pages, better user understanding and a more professional online presence.
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section id="contact" class="contact">
      <div class="wrapper">
        <h2 class="section-title">Get in touch</h2>
        <p>
          Want help improving your website content, layout or clarity? Get in touch to discuss what needs fixing.
        </p>
        <p>
          Email: <a href="mailto:hello@siteclarity.co.uk">hello@siteclarity.co.uk</a>
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>

  <footer>
    <div class="wrapper">
      <p>&copy; 2026 Site Clarity. All rights reserved.</p>
    </div>
  </footer>

</body>
</html>
